HEADWORD: White slave
<hw>White slave</hw>. <def>A woman held in involuntary confinement for
purposes of prostitution; loosely, any woman forced into unwilling
prostitution.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>White slaver</ent>⟦br⟧
